title: HourFace.Paid.Apk
description: This App reminds me of how sketch artists add age to a person to see how they would look after missing for years. Upload a pic of yourself or a friend and add age to their face to see how they might look years from now. Has an adjustment bar to increase the age as too how old you might want to make the person. There's no cropping or photo editing like that. So if you're looking for a photo editor don't bother with this torrent. This is just a fun App to take a photo and add age to it. Maybe post a friends pic on FaceBook with age added. If you enjoy the App please re-seed.
